data.description: Welcome to your new home.  This most desirable townhome is 20 minutes from midtown, just off I-75. This modern home with floor-to-ceiling windows is what you have been waiting for. Luxury townhome living with open floor plans just 2 miles from the Battery! This beautifully appointed 3-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home has a two-car garage (and two car driveway), 10-foot-high ceilings, top-of-the-line tile, hardwood flooring, quartz countertops, solid wood cabinetry with soft-close features, and stainless steel appliances.   This home boasts a private deck on each level. You must see the large fourth-level owner's suite with freestanding tub! The home also includes a terrace level guest suite with a private deck. You will love entertaining and relaxing at the 15-foot-long island. Going out is easy too - shopping, and some of the city's best restaurants are nearby. This home will go quickly, you don't want to miss out!
